message.body: Hey! How late you gonna be up tonight??
I am at a rehearsal for my recital, but was gonna grab a few things at the grocery and bring them to your house...
We are lounging in bed watching a movie. I'm prolly gonna pass out early cause I got up so early!
Hope recital practice went well!!
Ok no worries!
See you tomorrow!! :)
See ya tmw! Looking forward to it!!!
Me too! Gonna eat so much key lime!
Hey! We decided not to go out to eat tonight so I can clean so come over anytime! Can be later than 1 if you've got stuff to do.
Cool. Will probably be closer to 1:30 :)
Have a bunch of shit to bring so gonna load up car and drive to you!
Haha! I can give you a hand if you need!!
Awesome! I had that step class last night and it's a little hard to walk today :/
Ahahaha. I can't wait to hear about it!
Getting some packages together that I have to run to post office
Will come over after!
Cool!!! I'm in the back yard!
Gonna run this package to post office now, but gonna drop a few things at your place on the way!
Front door is open come on in!
Cool!
I should've helped hang banners!
Oh I forgot! I'll do one on the left and one in the right!
Thanks!! :)
